@prefix narr: <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .

GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ArchitectureOverview> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ArchitectureOverview> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#ArchitectureOverview> ;
    narr:childCount "41"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "9cecc1fa54e811e4d98f2db09af3cfa87c3e4e84" ;
    narr:narration """The architecture has evolved from a directory-based compilation model toward a [transform-based perspective engine](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TransformOverQuery), prioritizing [pure-function workflows](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PureFunctionArchitecture) where orchestrators manage all side effects. Identity is anchored to [phone numbers](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_IdentityViaPhone), with [group-based repositories](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_GroupAsRepo) serving as the primary unit of institutional memory. Recent refinements emphasize [in-memory graph storage](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GraphInMemoryStorage) to decouple from GitHub dependencies, while the [perspective response structure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveResponseOrderedByVolatility) now enforces a fixed, volatility-ordered layout. The [digest itself](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DigestAsRecognitionAid) has become the primary navigation surface, replacing embedded snapshots to ensure [visibility invariants](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_VisibilityInvariantAreaIndex) across all consumers. While the [named perspective architecture](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_NamedPerspectiveArchitecture) allows for sub-agent consultation, the system faces a known [conviction-temporality gap](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConvictionStackTemporalityGap) that has triggered production failures, alongside an open design question regarding [implication-based perspective navigation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ImplicationConceptProvisional).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_GroupAsRepo> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_IdentityViaPhone> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CodeAsCompilationOutput> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CompileTimeActorLens> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConvictionStackTemporalityGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DataHandlingSubstantiated> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DigestAsRecognitionAid> ;
